labels.en: Immersed Tunnel Ontology - Geotechnical and Foundation Systems

comments.en:
Enhanced geotechnical analysis and foundation systems for immersed tunnels.
            Comprehensive soil analysis, foundation design, and ground improvement.
            Based on GB/T 51318-2019 and JTG 2120-2020 Chapter 9-10 standards.
            
            CONSOLIDATES:
            - Geotechnical analysis from geotechnical_analysis.owl
            - Foundation systems from foundation_systems_components.owl
            - Soil investigation and characterization
            - Ground improvement and treatment methods
            
            ENHANCEMENTS:
            - Advanced geotechnical modeling
            - Foundation optimization
            - Ground treatment strategies
            - Stability analysis methods
